snippet.title: Apex Legends Season 6 – Boosted Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Apex Legends Season 6 – Boosted introduces a new Legend: Rampart, new weapon, fresh Battle Pass, Ranked and more! http://x.ea.com/64060

Build your rep in Apex Legends Season 6 - Boosted. New Legend Rampart has arrived to upgrade the competition. Unearth a new way to grab better gear with the new Crafting system. Ready to charge into battle? Get amped for the new Volt energy SMG. The leaves are falling and the rockets are rising on World’s Edge -- explore a revamped map and use the new Blast Walls to your advantage. Grab the new Battle Pass to instantly access exclusive items like the Legendary Sentinel Rollcage skin and three new Rare Legends skins. Then battle through Daily and Weekly Challenges to earn unique rewards like the new Holo-Sprays, Apex Packs, XP Boosts, and skins. If you’re up for a true test of skill, hone your craft in Season 6 Ranked. Get out there and show the Outlands what you’re made of!  

Apex Legends™ is a free-to-play battle royale game where legendary characters battle for glory, fame, and fortune on the fringes of the Frontier. Play for free now on Xbox One, PS4, and Origin for PC.

snippet.title: The Devil All The Time starring Tom Holland & Robert Pattinson | Official Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
Some people are just born to be buried. 

In Knockemstiff, Ohio and its neighboring backwoods, sinister characters — an unholy preacher (Robert Pattinson), twisted couple (Jason Clarke and Riley Keough), and crooked sheriff (Sebastian Stan) — converge around young Arvin Russell (Tom Holland) as he fights the evil forces that threaten him and his family. Spanning the time between World War II and the Vietnam war, director Antonio Campos’ THE DEVIL ALL THE TIME renders a seductive and horrific landscape that pits the just against the corrupted. Co-starring Bill Skarsgård, Mia Wasikowska, Harry Melling, Haley Bennett, and Pokey LaFarge, this suspenseful, finely-woven tale is adapted from Donald Ray Pollock's award-winning novel.

Watch The Devil All The Time at https://netflix.com/thedevilallthetime

snippet.title: Christina Aguilera - Loyal Brave True (From "Mulan"/Official Video)
snippet.description:
Stream Disney’s Mulan September 4 exclusively on Disney+ with Premier Access. Additional fee required. More info: http://disneyplus.com/mulan

“Loyal Brave True”
Performed by Christina Aguilera (@xtina) From Mulan (Original Motion Picture Soundtrack) Download/stream it here: https://disneymusic.co/Mulan?iqid=dmvevo ⚔ 

⚔ ⚔ When the Emperor of China issues a decree that one man per family must serve in the Imperial Army to defend the country from Northern invaders, Hua Mulan, the eldest daughter of an honored warrior, steps in to take the place of her ailing father. Masquerading as a man, Hua Jun, she is tested every step of the way and must harness her inner-strength and embrace her true potential. It is an epic journey that will transform her into an honored warrior and earn her the respect of a grateful nation…and a proud father. “Mulan” features a celebrated international cast that includes: Yifei Liu as Mulan; Donnie Yen as Commander Tung; Jason Scott Lee as Böri Khan; Yoson An as Cheng Honghui; with Gong Li as Xianniang and Jet Li as the Emperor. The film is directed by Niki Caro from a screenplay by Rick Jaffa & Amanda Silver and Elizabeth Martin & Lauren Hynek based on the narrative poem “The Ballad of Mulan.”

snippet.title: Me. Painting on Things.
snippet.description:
Hey guys! So today’s video is….a little different. I was feeling a little overwhelmed with ideas (aka super spazzy, sorry about the intro lol) and so I decided to just kind of have a free for all today and not plan anything in advance….in order to avoid commitment hhaa. I gave myself a bunch of options for different art activities to do including painting squishies, making custom pencil pouches, painting on tote bags, decorating seashells, rock painting, custom painting vans, my sketchbook, decorating outlet covers etc. All of these I’ve done at some point on my channel. Some of them have become my kinda go-to, and some of them I hadn’t done in quite a while.

This is kinda like a spazzy paint with me video 🤣 But, hopefully it can give you some fun ideas for things to customize. All of these are cheap things that make for super fun painting projects.


SHOP NEW PRODUCTS: https://moriahelizabethmerch.com/



Stuff I'm Using *affiliate links*:
Posca Fine Liner: https://amzn.to/30U8nE4
Angelus Leather Paint: https://amzn.to/3h3Pzbe
Fancy Watercolors: https://amzn.to/33YqHh5
Colored Pencils: https://amzn.to/326z7kf


___________WELCOME TO MY CHANNEL__________

Hey! my name is Moriah (pronounced muh-rye-yuh 😂 ) and this is my channel....obviously. I'm 25 and like doing anything creative...and being snarky.....just a lil. I make a lot of decorating and painting videos here. I'm obsessed with editing and adding lil bits to my videos, so if that's not your thing....oof you may hate this haha. I paint on squishies, thrift store finds, and other random things I pick up. I also love to draw, but don't expect anything too skilled, I'm not the best at that haha. You will also find occasional crafting/testing crafting kits on my channel which are always a hot mess. And even some baking (REALLY bad at that, but it's fun to try LOL). 

CURRENT SERIES:
Squishy Makeovers: Fixing and decorating used squishies sent from my viewers
Thrift Store Makeovers: Fixing and decorating stuff I find at thrift stores/yard sales
Bake With ME: Recreating squishies I've decorated in real life
Create This Book: Drawing in the prompt book that I wrote (available to purchase and follow along)
Squishy Unboxing: Opening used squishy packages sent from viewers
Craft Kit Testing: pretty self explanatory. testing craft kits.



___UPLOAD SCHEDULE___

Every Friday at 4:00pm ET: Alternating Squishy Makeovers, Thrift Makeovers, Craft Kit Reviews, Create This Book, Mail Openings and Miscellaneous crafts and DIYs

https://amzn.to/2vUerfI

https://moriahelizabethmerch.com/

____ME SOCIALS____

https://www.instagram.com/moriahelizabethofficial/

TIKTOK:
https://www.tiktok.com/@me.moriah.elizabeth

VISIT ME WEBSITE:
https://www.moriahelizabeth.com/


____CONTACT ME____

EMAIL PICTURES OF YOUR ART (Create This Book or Fan art only please):
Artwork@Moriah.video

FOR BUSINESS INQUIRIES/OPPORTUNITIES ONLY:
Business@Moriah.video


_____MAIL ME_____

For sending squishies, Letters, or general fan mail, please contact: FANMAIL@MORIAH.VIDEO to request my P.O. box address 
(must be 13+ to send mail)
ATTENTION: Unfortunately I can only respond to a small amount of people each week. This is to make sure that I get a reasonable amount of mail and can feature the maximum amount on camera. I apologize in advance if you do not hear back from me, I may not have even seen the message. This email gets SUPER clogged with thousands of messages. Currently have 15,000+ unread messages just in this folder. SORRY PEEPS!*

snippet.title: sewing a dress from scratch *project runway i'm ready*
snippet.description:
inspired by avrey ovard's video! ➭ https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_QL8Pitidzw
instagram  ➭ @best.dressed
OUTFITS LINKED BELOW ⇩⇩⇩
✨my jewelry collection ➭ https://enroutejewelry.com/collections/bestdressed
shop my presets ➭ https://www.bestdressedstore.com
my second channel ➭ http://bit.ly/bestmess
twitter ➭ @bestdressed
tik tok lol ➭ @bestdressed

After many years of thrift flipping, and even more years of watching Project Runway, I finally decided to face my fear of rolled hems and invisible zippers, and try to sew clothing from scratch. I bought some vintage dress patterns from the 1950’s, and with the help of my trusty sewing machine, the DIY moms of youtube, and way too much caffeine, I managed to sew a brand new summer dress from scratch. And it looks pretty darn good, as long as you stay more than six feet away.


✰ SEWING SUPPLIES ✰
my fabric scissors (i swear by these: https://amzn.to/3aroV9t)
sewing machine (https://amzn.to/2SNSub2)
fabric i used (https://bit.ly/2CoUAvI)
vintage patterns (https://bit.ly/3aoS1q6, https://bit.ly/2POKKpU)


✰ OUTFITS ✰
INTRO + SHOPPING OUTFIT
t-shirt: vintage from @shop_suki on instagram (similar: https://bit.ly/3kGzDh6)
pants: other stories (https://bit.ly/3cetfZn, similar: https://bit.ly/33QzjGr)
gold hoops + necklace: mejuri (http://youtube.mejuri.com/bestdressed)
mask: oh seven days (https://bit.ly/3auvvfC)

SEWING OUTFIT
pink cardigan: aritzia (sold out, similar: https://bit.ly/31PHGQ3, https://bit.ly/31PHGQ3)
shorts: agolde (https://bit.ly/3iBB0Me, more affordable + on sale: https://bit.ly/3gWW3bD)
pearl headband: jenn im x 8 other reasons (https://bit.ly/2PS6Ojw)

EDITING OUTFIT
top (similar: https://bit.ly/2CpUGTP)
glasses: wary parker (https://bit.ly/3edb4p1)
hair bow: urban outfitters (https://bit.ly/2CG3C7D)
 
FINAL TRY ON CLIPS
dress: sewn by me obvs :)
butterfly clips (https://amzn.to/3eVZhdv)
earrings: jenn im x 8 other reasons (https://bit.ly/2Yf8TuL)


✰ BEDROOM DECOR ✰
hanging flowers (https://amzn.to/3fYeBXE)
bedsheets: urban outfitters (sold out, similar: https://bit.ly/3fWRLQh)
pillow cases: urban outfitters (https://bit.ly/3fU1aYV)


♫ MUSIC ♫
diamonds and pearls by dezaulait (https://soundcloud.com/dezaulait/diamonds-and-pearls)
working at the mall + blackberry pie songs by @maxwell.landry on tik tok
lady by jeff kaale (https://soundcloud.com/jeff-kaale/lady)
esquimaux by rogyr (https://soundcloud.com/rogiermuller/esquimaux_ep)
just like a child by maxwell young (https://soundcloud.com/maxwell_young/just-like-a-child)
flashback by jeff kaale and danny mankind (https://soundcloud.com/dannymankind/flashback-feat-rufflemak-julida-remix-unedited)
great days by joakim karud (https://soundcloud.com/joakimkarud/great-days)
morning by S T H + Jeff Kaale + Jrco (https://soundcloud.com/sadiqthehonest/sadiq-jeff-jrco)
STH's youtube: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCmw60nuV2rPXzW7NcJhMj8w
charlie brown’s day off by louie zong (https://louiezong.bandcamp.com/track/charlie-browns-day-off) 


✰ FAQ ✰
what’s your name? ashley
what’s your instagram? @best.dressed
how old are you? 22 (born in 1998)
how tall are you? 5'5"
what’s your ethnicity? half british and half burmese
what equipment do you use to film?
 ➭  main camera: panasonic lumix gh5s (https://amzn.to/2Nb0W1z)
 ➭  8-18 mm lens (https://amzn.to/3bmVoxd)
 ➭  12-35mm lens (https://amzn.to/2JiSrz7)
 ➭  on camera mic: rode videomic pro+ (https://amzn.to/2QHfZBU)
 ➭  voiceover mic: blue yeti usb mic (https://go.magik.ly/ml/yshp/)
 ➭  vlog camera: canon g7x mark ii (http://amzn.to/2DfL4cZ)
 ➭  canon m50 (https://amzn.to/2Dp1bnk)
 ➭  editing: final cut pro

snippet.title: Action Bronson Shakes It Out While Eating Spicy Wings | Hot Ones
snippet.description:
Action Bronson—the  rapper, TV host, chef and New York Times Best Selling author—is back in the hot seat for round two of Hot Ones. You know him from his show ‘F*ck That’s Delicious,’ and his new album ‘Only For Dolphins’ is on the way with the single “Latin Grammys” out now. How will Bam Bam fare against the Season 12 hot sauce lineup? Find out how Mr. Wonderful does against the heat while talking about his quarantine workouts, Star Wars vs. Indiana Jones, abstract art, acting roles and being directed by Judd Apatow (‘The King of Staten Island’) and Martin Scorsese (‘The Irishman’), and why Billy Joel is the best lyricist ever. It’s the return of Action Bronson, a Hot Ones legend and Hot Ones family for life! Bonus: Action shares his recipe for the perfect quarantine sandwich!

Check out more of First We Feast here:
